# AutoX Test Automation

When writing or editing AutoX test XML in this project, follow these rules.

## Required reading

Before creating or modifying test suite XML, read:

1. `docs/autox-llm/README.md` ŌĆö documentation index
2. `docs/autox-llm/reference/README.md` ŌĆö API reference index by Group
3. The relevant how-to guide and API reference for your task type (see table below)

