| REST API | `07-rest-automation.md` | `reference/steps-rest-api.md` | `reference/validations-rest-api.md` |
| UI / Selenium | `08-ui-automation.md` | `reference/steps-ui.md` | `reference/validations-ui.md` |
| Data-driven tests | `05-data-providers.md` | (per step group) | (per step group) |
| Expressions / `${...}` | `06-expressions.md` | `reference/prefix-expressions.md`, `reference/freemarker-methods.md` | ŌĆö |
